column3: “Great strain! Try it for yourself as I highly recommend it if you can get your hands on it.”

““Hands down dopest dope I’ve ever smoked.” To quote one of my favorite movies of all time. This strain packs a powerful punch not only to your head and body but honestly to your capability to actually hold yourself together to even have a normal conversation after smoking this. This strain Found mainly in the Pacific Northwest. It’s a must have. Also just to elaborate how strong this strain is I’ve smoked a good amou...”
“Always looking for strains that don't make me anxious or paranoid, this is just a good happy and relaxed weed. Going to stock up on it for sure.”
